Living with one Moves (23)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par It is one among the basic life and death problems but if White misses the first move, it is easy to capture him.
\par
\par The question is always the same, should White play inside or expand the living space?
\par }
