Dia. 01 Black 2, Mistake
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White expands his living space with 1.
\par If Black plays at 2, White lives with 3.
\par
\par After Black A, White takes with B and he is safe.
\par
\par However White lived because\cf1\b  Black 2 was bad\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par
\par
\par }
