Dia. 02 Death in Hane
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par "\cf1\b There is death in the hane\cf0\b0 " proverb is useful this time.
\par
\par First White plays at 2 and then Black's placement at 3 is the right order of the moves.
\par
\par 4 and 5 are miai so White can't live.
\par }
